msgstr "Exclure les produits gratuits et les commandes %s0"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:799
msgid "MemberPress is not properly loaded."
msgstr "MemberPress ne se charge pas correctement."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:809
msgid "Membership Tier Filtering"
msgstr "Filtrage par niveau d'adhésion"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:811
msgid ""
"Select which membership tiers should trigger review requests. Leave all "
"unchecked to include all memberships."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez les niveaux d'adhésion qui doivent déclencher des demandes de "
"révision. Ne cochez aucune case pour inclure tous les niveaux d'adhésion."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:825
msgid "No memberships found."
msgstr "Aucune adhésion trouvée."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:830
msgid "Review Request Timing"
msgstr "Calendrier des demandes d'examen"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:833
msgid "Send review request after:"
msgstr "Envoyer une demande d'avis après :"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:840
msgid "7 days"
msgstr "7 jours"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:842
msgid "14 days"
msgstr "14 jours"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:844
msgid "30 days"
msgstr "30 jours"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:848
msgid ""
"Allow members time to experience your content before requesting a review."
msgstr ""
"Laissez aux membres le temps de découvrir votre contenu avant de leur "
"demander de le noter."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:868
msgid "No Supported Services Detected"
msgstr "Aucun service pris en charge détecté"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:871
msgid "TrustScript works with WooCommerce, MemberPress, and more."
msgstr ""
"TrustScript est compatible avec WooCommerce, MemberPress et bien d'autres."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:874 trustscript.php:183
msgid "Install and activate a supported plugin to start collecting reviews."
msgstr ""
"Installez et activez un plugin compatible pour commencer à recueillir des "
"avis."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:877 trustscript.php:185
msgid "View Supported Platforms"
msgstr "Voir les plateformes prises en charge"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:887
msgid "Detected Services"
msgstr "Services détectés"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:888
msgid ""
"TrustScript has detected the following services on your site. Configure "
"trigger statuses for each service to automatically collect reviews."
msgstr ""
"TrustScript a détecté les services suivants sur votre site. Configurez les "
"statuts de déclenchement pour chaque service afin de collecter "
"automatiquement les avis."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:921
msgid "Trigger Status:"
msgstr "État du déclencheur :"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:923
msgid "Send review request when order reaches this status"
